# [LSR](../wg/lsr.html)

## Summary

The Link State Routing (LSR) Working Group met at IETF 126. The session covered working group status updates, including document progression, followed by presentations and technical discussions on power-aware routing, security/replay protection, database synchronization, active measurement provisioning, traffic engineering for microbursts, distributed congestion mitigation, egress protection, and process ID verification.

---

## Key Discussion Points

